high_descs: Turn right and move towards the end of the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn right and move to the microwave on your left.
Put the knife in the microwave in front of the egg.
Turn left and head back to the end of the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn right and move to the fridge on your right.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge on the left shelf for a few seconds and then take it back out.
Turn around and head back to the microwave on your left.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled piece of bread in the microwave with a knife.

high_descs: Turn right, go across the room and turn right at the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the bread.
Cut the bread with the knife.
Turn right and then head left to the stove.
Put the knife in the microwave above the stove.
Turn left and go back to the end of the counter with the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right and head to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick up the bread.
Turn around and turn left to head to the stove.
Put the bread in the microwave above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter
Pick up the butterknife on the kitchen counter
Cut the loaf of bread on the kitchen counter
Walk to the microwave
Put the butterknife in the microwave
Walk back to the counter where the sliced bread is
Pick up a slice of bread
Go to the fridge
Chill the slice of bread in the fridge
Go to the microwave
Put the bread slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a butterknife and a chilled slice of bread in a microwave
